Interface TrafficManagementCenterOperatingSystem

All Superinterfaces:
CellCommunicative, OperatingSystem, Routable, ServerOperatingSystem
All Known Implementing Classes:
TrafficManagementCenterUnit
public interface TrafficManagementCenterOperatingSystem extends ServerOperatingSystem
This interface extends the basic OperatingSystem and is implemented by the AbstractSimulationUnit TrafficManagementCenterUnit.

    • changeVariableMessageSignState

      TrafficManagementCenterOperatingSystem.ChangeLaneState changeVariableMessageSignState(String signId, int laneIndex)
      Provides a facility to change the lane state of a Variable Message Sign (VMS).
      Parameters:
      signId - The ID of the sign.
      laneIndex - The index of the lane (0 = right-most lane). For speed assignments a negative lane index is allowed, addressing all lanes.
